            "text": "The DVWA login form does not implement any account lockout, rate limiting, or brute-force protection. Ten consecutive failed login attempts for the admin account all returned the same generic \"Login failed\" response with HTTP 302 redirect to login.php. No CAPTCHA was presented, no lockout occurred, and no delay was introduced between attempts. This enables unlimited brute-force attacks against any account."
